 it, as well, but here again, I thought that Black has very little chance to play for a win in the main tabiya of the variation that arises after6.Be2Bf57.O-ONd78.Nf3e69.c4N5f610.Nh4Bg611.g3Still, this is a very solid setup, so if you want to keep things flexible and mix it up every now and then - I can only recommend you to check this variation in greater detail.} 
