43. Kf7 {And here we agreed to a draw. At first glance, a relatively colorless game, where neither player excelled by any means. Still, considering this was my first ever tournament game and that I faced a higher-rated player AND that I knew no theory at all, I do consider it a big success.I hope you will too - or that you at least got some laughs at my expense as I was taking you down this memory lane.} 
